upper bound. 

-there is cplex at root node

- pricing problem with label limit for non processed labels is used.

Options:
1. a) After 2nd espprc, call domination b)do not call domination algorithm. 
2. a) After 1st espprc, before 2nd espprc, do threshold in domination 
   b) do not use domination
3. a)In 2nd espprc, in intermediate steps domination algorithm wiht NO 
   LL
   b) Have label limit
4. a) In 2nd espprc, in intermediate steps, do not do domination, add
  F to LabelList[j]
   b) do domination 

Experiments with p01-f25-v1t1.txt, p03-l25-v1t1.txt, p01-l25-v1t1.txt
1a and 1 b exact pricing all the time, later in 2,3,4 label limit 30 then 
60 is used.
